about.summary: Creates an interactive scatterplot matrix using the D3 JavaScript library. See <http://d3js.org/> for more information on D3.

name: r-pairsd3
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '0.1.0' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-pairsd3
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/pairsD3_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/pairsD3/pairsD3_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 02a37d885dd25e6ce74eff90aa87628113585d71158ad2a27797082723be8662

build:
  noarch: generic
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 1002
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:

  host:
    - r-base
    - r-htmlwidgets >=0.3.2
    - r-shiny
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-htmlwidgets >=0.3.2
    - r-shiny

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('pairsD3')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('pairsD3')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: http://github.com/garthtarr/pairsD3/
  license: GPL (>= 3)
  summary: Creates an interactive scatterplot matrix using the D3 JavaScript library. See <http://d3js.org/>
    for more information on D3.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file: '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-3'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
